      summary:
        'Peanut Butter and Apple Oatmeal Breakfast Bars takes around <b>45 minutes</b> from beginning to end. Watching your figure? This lacto ovo vegetarian recipe has <b>288 calories</b>, <b>7g of protein</b>, and <b>11g of fat</b> per serving. This recipe serves 8 and costs 49 cents per serving. A few people made this recipe, and 15 would say it hit the spot. It works well as a very reasonably priced breakfast. It is brought to you by Foodista. If you have apple, honey, vanillan extract, and a few other ingredients on hand, you can make it. With a spoonacular <b>score of 43%</b>, this dish is solid. If you like this recipe, you might also like recipes such as <a href="https://spoonacular.com/recipes/peanut-butter-and-apple-oatmeal-breakfast-bars-1409137">Peanut Butter and Apple Oatmeal Breakfast Bars</a>, <a href="https://spoonacular.com/recipes/peanut-butter-and-apple-oatmeal-breakfast-bars-1300603">Peanut Butter and Apple Oatmeal Breakfast Bars</a>, and <a href="https://spoonacular.com/recipes/caramel-apple-peanut-butter-oatmeal-bars-1320853">Caramel Apple Peanut Butter Oatmeal Bars</a>.',
